c: 61
v: 5
t: "Yabona uMûsâ wathi kubantu bakubo: “Hini na bantu bakuthi, nindikhubekiselani na nisazi ngokuqinisekileyo nje okokuba mna ndinguMthunywa ka-Allâh kuni?” Ke kaloku bathi besakuphambuka, uAllâh Wenza iintliziyo zabo zaphambuka. Ke kaloku uAllâh Akabakhokeli abadelelayo, abangenantobeko"